      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-shopify card mt-8">
      <h2>SMS operations depth 3: email-SMS collision rules for…</h2>
      <p>For <strong>alternatives shopify email alternative</strong>, email-SMS collision rules for cart recovery and product launches is not optional infrastructure. Shopify SMS apps that recover urgent revenue without wrecking consent treat every text as a scarce interrupt — cart recovery after meaningful checkout intent, launch access for opted-in VIPs, replenishment when SKU usage data supports timing.</p>
