      <h2>SMS operations depth 4: weekly SMS caps per…</h2>
      <p>For <strong>alternatives shopify email alternative</strong>, weekly SMS caps per subscriber before broadcast approval tiers is not optional infrastructure. Shopify SMS apps that recover urgent revenue without wrecking consent treat every text as a scarce interrupt — cart recovery after meaningful checkout intent, launch access for opted-in VIPs, replenishment when SKU usage data supports timing.</p>
